data.description: Located on almost an acre lot, country peaceful living but close to the city, I-49, Shopping, Healthcare, Stores. No-thru traffic, dead end street. Completely remodeled in 2022! Large, 1,961 heated SQFT home with 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, sunroom office or playroom in back, front flex room with closet could be nursery, dayroom, or 4th bedroom if needed. New carpet in 2022, new lighting, new plumbing fixtures, nice vinyl plank floors, kitchen has beautiful granite countertops, refrigerator remains, built in wine rack, washer and dryer remain in laundry room. Living room has wood burning fireplace. NO HOA!! Storage shed outside, Nice large covered workshop and storage for boats, ATVs, toys. Partially fenced. Plenty of land behind the current workshop to build more if needed. *Not in a Flood Zone* Call today for your private showing
